With his brother Denzell, he formed the famous dance duo 'Villi Manilli' back in 20th century. At the top of their popularity they both vanished. The reason was a scandal where the media discovered that they didn't perform their songs, and that Sam was really the main vocalist. The world was laughing at them. But the brothers laughed at world. Denzell and Gregory were the coolest people that Sam had ever met, so he offered them to join him in saving a world. Now they bring fun and coolness into the Sam's squadron.
